{"title":"家书","authors":["刘英冲"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":9,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"家书"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘英冲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我想念你！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岛上多少昶日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在码头伫立"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祈祷蓝天：能把你的照片"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"折射到我的泪光里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你一定记得："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿早已超过了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"离开你时你的年纪；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你知道吗？有一天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我呼唤妈妈的声音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把岛上的树叶震落了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它带着我的问候飘向了你。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听儿告诉你："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每当岛上的夜风在树尖打起口哨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我便躲进梦里去见你；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这时，你慈祥的脸庞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总是挂着含泪的微笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"故乡的山，故乡的人，故乡的老井，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也都向我张开温暖的怀抱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢迎我，拥抱我；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我流泪，枕头也流泪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你再等等我吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国就要统一，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿和你就快团聚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许明天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我就能回去看你。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（作者单位：辽宁抚顺市第一毛纺厂）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}